ABUJA- The Department of State Services (DSS) has alerted the Public on plans by criminal elements to carry out violent attacks on public places, including key and vulnerable points during Yuletide season. The Service revealed this in a statement signed by its Spokesperson, Peter Afunanya on Tuesday, at Abuja. According to the statement, the Service explained that, “The planned dastardly acts are to be executed through the use of explosives, suicide bombing and other dangerous weapons. EXPOSED - HOW LAGOS DOCTOR DISCOVERED MAJOR REASONS WHY MOST WIVES NOW HEAVILY CHEATS ON THEIR HUSBANDS AND THE PERMANENT SECRET TO SEXUALLY SATISFYING THEIR WIVES. DON'T BE A VICTIM! “The objective is to create a general sense of fear among the people and subsequently undermine the Government.” Against this backdrop, the DSS urged citizens to be extra vigilant and report strange movements and indeed, all suspicions around them to security and law enforcement agencies. NEMA Urges Motorists To Observe Speed Limit, Road Signs Yuletide: FRSC Deploys 1,250 Personnel In Enugu The Service further stated that, it is collaborating with other sister agencies to ensure that adequate measures are put in place for protection of lives and property. To further achieve this purpose, the Service has therefore provided the following emergency response numbers, 08132222105 and 09030002189 for urgent contacts. It also used the opportunity to unveil its interactive website www.dss.gov.ng for public communication support. It said, “Everyone is encouraged to take advantage of these platforms and similar ones provided by related agencies to timely reach and avail them (security agencies) of required information.” However, the Service advised those planning to cause chaos and damage to public peace to desist from such as it will stop at nothing to apprehend and bring them to justice. While assuring citizens and residents of their safety during and after the festive periods, the Director General of DSS, Alhaji YM. Bichi, with his Management and Staff, wished all, Happy Celebrations and a Prosperous 2021. SHOCKING! DOCTORS ARE MESMERIZED BY THIS NATURAL PREMATURE EJACULATION AND SMALL SIZE SOLUTION GUARANTEED TO BULLDOZE YOUR WOMAN INTO SEXUAL SUBMISSION